export const questionObj = {"Qtext": "
 
Find the mean proportion of 6.3 and 0.7 
\newline

", "Steps": [{"id": "s1", "n_params": 0, "step_txt": "
 
The mean proportion of 6.3 and 0.7 is $\sqrt{6.3 \times 0.7 }$.
\[
	= \sqrt{\frac{63.0 \times 7.0 }{100}} = \frac{21 }{10} = 2.1 
\]
Since, 
\[
	63.0 \times 7.0 = 441 = 21 ^2
\]
\newline

"}]}
